#########################################################
# PlanWise - Views Directory Protection
# Location: /views/
#
# Purpose: Prevent direct access to view files
#          Views should only be included by controllers/routers
#########################################################

# Deny all direct access
Order Deny,Allow
Deny from all

# Prevent directory listing
Options -Indexes

#########################################################
# Security Rationale:
#########################################################
# View files should never be accessed directly because:
# 1. They may contain PHP code that expects certain variables
# 2. They don't have authentication checks
# 3. Direct access bypasses routing and middleware
# 4. Can expose application structure
#
# Views are meant to be included by:
# - public/index.php (main router)
# - Controllers (after authentication/authorization)
#########################################################
